ta-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104evy1665702700672.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/evy1665702700672.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/evy1665702700672.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"evy1665702700672\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Working With Structs: Code Examples\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"evy1665702700672__working_with_structscode_examples_61584\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To illustrate how Structs can be manipulated, you can inspect and execute the following ProcScript examples.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"evy1665702700672__p_d18287e1_d18288e1_d18289e1\">For a case study in which data is converted from XML to\n      Uniface component entities and back again, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yeb1665702700742.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yeb1665702700742.html\" title=\"This example uses Struct manipulation to transform incoming XML data into Uniface entities so that the data can be updated, and transform it back to original XML format.\">Example: Struct Conversions</a>. </p>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"evy1665702700672__note_w145ab1b5b5_w146ab1b5_w147ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> For your convenience, you can copy the code of all the examples from <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hrj1665702700815.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hrj1665702700815.html\" title=\"You can copy and paste the code in this topic into a Uniface trigger or operation (such as the exec operation of a test component).\">Struct Code Examples</a> and paste it into a Uniface trigger or operation (such as the\n      EXEC operation of a test component). Compile the component, test it, and view the message\n      frame to see the output.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"evy1665702700672__topic_d13037e1_d13038e1_d13039e1_d13040e1_d13041e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d957194e76\"> Print Header Function </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"evy1665702700672__p_d18293e1_d18294e1_d18295e1\">This is a utility function that use by the other examples\n        to provide a header.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">function printHeader\nparams\n string pFunctionName : IN\nendparams\n putmess \"===============================\"\n putmess \" run of %%pFunctionName%%%\"\n putmess \"===============================\"\n \nend ;- function printHeader</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612912\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612912\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Working With Structs: Code Examples Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Working With Structs: Code Examples To illustrate how Structs can be manipulated, you can inspect and execute the following ProcScript examples. For a case study in which data is converted from XML to Uniface component entities and back again, see Example: Struct Conversions . Tip: For your convenience, you can copy the code of all the examples from Struct Code Examples and paste it into a Uniface trigger or operation (such as the EXEC operation of a test component). Compile the component, test it, and view the message frame to see the output. Print Header Function This is a utility function that use by the other examples to provide a header. function printHeader params string pFunctionName : IN endparams putmess \"===============================\" putmess \" run of %%pFunctionName%%%\" putmess \"===============================\" end ;- function printHeader Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}